\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 23, Toxteth Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And you're a widower aren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What year were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 1880.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What year were you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 ?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 1902.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember how many years you lived in the house in which you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you live in there 'til 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Wait a bit. 1918 - no, wait a bit. I'd be what - eight - I'd be twenty - no, I'd be eighteen wouldn't I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You'd be thirty-eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, I'd - I was not in Toxteth Street then, I left Toxteth Street about fourteen as near as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Why did you leave Toxteth Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well me father moved to another neighbourhood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Any idea why he moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He went to High Park Street,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was it a bigger house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Bigger house, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Is that the only move your father made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh no, he made two or three but still - that's where I finished up until I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh I think there was eight - well me mother - me mother had eleven children but - three - three - two of them I don't remember. All 
I know that this - I was told it, but - one died as a lad in seven years of age - seven years and seven months I believe. Well when me mother died she left eight of us. You see there's six of us still living. And she died in 1893 so that's an unusual.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Could you give me any idea when they were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well I can tell you the ages of what are living now, but that - the - of the - of the eight I can give you the day - the dates of them but one of the three that died in infancy. But - But I can give you the eldest lad was born March the twenty-sixth 1876.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was his name?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 John - John.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Kitty. Girl. She was born December the twelfth 1877.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 After that - well the next one - William, was born April the twentieth '79.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Myself. October 1880.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the next one after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - except - wait a bit - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 
1885 in}}}1885 in{\*\xmlclose} - in - September.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the next one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname metricconverter}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname ProductID}{\xmlattrvalue 1886 in}}}1886 in{\*\xmlclose}
 December.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there anymore then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Yes, there's two more - yes. And another sister in October 1888. And another sister in - 19 - July 19 - 1892. Now you should have eight there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When did you say your mother died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When? May the twenty-eighth '93.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 The youngest child was only twelve months old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 She was only ten months really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How old was your father when you were born - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Thirty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well as far as I know he was born in Liverpool but that I'm not quite sure. 
I'm not sure but I understand he was born in Liverpool but he - it would be the south end.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He was a - a checker at the docks. A ship checker. Of the col - a checker on the cargo boats really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he have another job before or after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He was there - well - he was in the flour mill but I don't know what his job was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he also have any casual or part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he always work on the docks until he died or 'til he retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Until he - until he went abroad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So you don't know what happened to him then do you? Did he go abroad and come back again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, he never came back again, he died there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was his job when he went abroad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He was in - well he was - as far 
as I know he had his own ground for like tilling the ground, I mean, what do you call work - looking after a - a ground, as far as I know for himself. He - I don't believe - worked for any firm - not that I know. Because I mean to say he was in fifties as
 near as I know when he went. But he bought a piece of ground and he cultivated that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Whereabouts was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In Canada.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You never saw him after he emigrated then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh no. Never saw him after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember your father being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only - only when the - was - the dock strike on. But not otherwise. 'Cos he had a - he - he had a regular job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How old was your mother when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When I was born? Well she'd be six years younger than me father. So - if he was born in - in 1918 - 1850 she was born - 19 - yes, 1856.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 She'd be about twenty-four wouldn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I think she was nineteen I understand but she was six years younger than me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He was thirty when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, he was thirty when I was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 She'd be twenty-four when you were born wouldn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, she'd be twenty-four, yes, I see what - yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did she come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 She was Liverpool - she was a Liverpool girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was her job before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I don't know - I never heard that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. She had too many children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How many rooms were in the house in High Park Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Now you've given me a puzzle there. There was -
 two cellar kitchens, there was two sitting rooms - next floor, on the ground floor, there was two bedrooms on the next floor and there were three bedrooms on the top floor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So there'd be two reception rooms weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, two reception rooms, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did anyone else besides your parents and brothers and sisters live in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother pay anybody to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Help me father out?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, did your mother pay anybody to do any housework for her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
That I couldn't say - she never did when she was well but whether she did otherwise because of course as the girls grew up they could help her. But she didn't have an outside help.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was the washing done at home or was it sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That was don
e at home. Funny question to ask that all the same. I know we had no outside help because we - as the girls grew up - they helped in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother or father mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Well - me mother - mother would make
 odd things but not make the regular things. She would make odd things. Such as now I can - I can only dimly rem - I don't know what she did but she had a sewing machine and she used to make us a round cap for school. Yes, I don't know - I can't explain -
 how but she did them on machine but I - whether she did any other I don't know - I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were the clothes you got new or second}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you buy them from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh that's hard to say 'cos I don't know}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Some people used to buy them from the market.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Oh no. I only have a dim recollection of us - the lads I mean - going to Lewis's. With me father. But of course that's only a dim recollection.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father repair your shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father help your mother with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of - 'cos there's plenty of girls, see, I don't think so there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he do any decorating in the house - any repairs or improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he dress or undress or bath any of the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh - not regular. He could do but he never did it regular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he look after you when your mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well she was never out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any jobs you had to carry out regularly at home to help your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well only Saturday I used to do the windows. And do - scrub - scrub the - swill the yard, but that's about all that I know of.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How long did you continue to do these tasks - after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Now that I don't know - I did them - I was going to school when I did them but I ca
n't tell whether - no, after I left school no I didn't because - when I went to work I didn't do any jobs in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your brothers and sisters have jobs also?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 They didn't have jobs in the house like you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh they would in turn. In turn, but not - not otherwise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the older children help the younger children with things they found difficult?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that I couldn't tell you - 'cos that was mostly the girls job so of course I couldn't tell you much about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the elder ones look after the younger ones - suppose you went to play, did they look after the younger ones when they went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I can't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the younger children help the older ones in any way - did you go messages for your elder brother or help your younger sisters at all?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I've no recollection really, I daresay we have done but I've no recollection of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well usually about nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We went to bed ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What age did you start going to bed yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I can't tell you. Don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you share the bedroom or bed with a brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What were the sleeping arrangements of the family? You had five bedrooms didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well there's - the girls - the girls they had - two bedrooms and the lads had two bedrooms and me - me father and mother had the other one.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Which room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We hadn't a bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well get a - get the bath downstairs and have a bath in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In which room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In the basement - down -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In one of those two cellar kitchens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, that's it - that's it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How often did you bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't - couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there a recognised bath night or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We - we usually had one every - every - weekend. But that'd be about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When did you put clean clothes on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Every Sun - every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - in the cellar kitchen mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any occasions when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 A christening or a wedding or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In the back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have a coal range or did you have gas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Now you're asking me a question because - gas wasn't invented then. Not as actually speaking, it was only when I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
 it was only in its infancy and we only had a gas ring - so I can't tell you - it was by fire here, it was by fire always. Because there was no gas - there was no gas, it was only in its infancy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 They were very big houses those weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 The one in High Park Street wes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 , yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 They were houses of the rich really weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I suppose they were eventually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When was breakfast eaten - was it eaten in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In the cellar kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you all together during breakfast time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - no, because me father had to go go work before we had our breakfast but - was with me mother we had it. Before then of course she saw that we went to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So your father had his breakfast beforehand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well he had to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You children and your mother}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 had your breakfast just before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you usually have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Bread and butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You were l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 ucky, we had bread and mar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 garine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well it may be margarine but I - that I don't know. We called it butter so we don't know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have anything different on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not that I know of. Unless it was a bit of bacon but I can't tell you whether we did or not - I'm not sure about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you have for your dinner - what would you call a midday meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that was the dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you generally have for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 I couldn't tell you s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
ave - the variety all I know it was potatoes and meat but I couldn't tell you what.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What about the evening meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that was bread and butter. Or perhaps jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your dad come home for dinner or did he come home at night time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Wait a bit. It was according where he worked. No, he - he came home for
 dinner time if he was working near but - if he wasn't well of course he'd have it at night time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It would be saved for him would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she bottle fruit or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Any wine or medicine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was any beer brewed in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father or mother grow their own vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No - 'cos we had no garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they buy tinned or dried vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they keep any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How many times a week did you eat meat?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that's hard to say because I mean to say me mother made the dinners and we didn't worry about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You must have had it pretty frequently otherwise you would have remembered wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - I - well I suppose it was with the dinner but I couldn't tell you what we had or anything in that sense. All we know, I know we had - we had meat but whether we had it every day I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember seeing your mother having less food so the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father have more food than the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I notice - not that I know of. We all had it together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, yes, to a certain extent. I mean to say, there}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 was no fixed - there was no fixed rules about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we never worried about - we just took what was given to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was your parents attitude if you left some food uneaten on the plate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We never left it. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What would have happened if you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 had have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We should - well - all according to what}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 it was. It was never wasted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If there was something on the table you wanted like the salt could you ask someone to pass it to you or did you have to wait 
until it was offered to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - just according to what was there. If it was bread and butter you could take it. If it was anything other you'd have to wait for it or would ask for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Salt or bread and butter you could take - you wouldn't have to wait until it was passed round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh no, not necessarily.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes, if we wanted to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we normally hold - held it in the ordinary way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Some people are more particular than others you know weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were your people particular about your table manners?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we were - we always behaved ourselves at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Could you bring a book to the table - could you read during a meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. I'm against that myself.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When we all - well - when - when we'd all finished eating, then we'd get up and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You couldn't get up before that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We didn't as a norm - as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did all the family sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well if they were in, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you always have the same places at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. Pretty well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How was the meal served - did your mother put the food in
 a tureen and put it on the plates or did she take it directly from the dish in which she cooked it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, but I'm just trying to think if she did. Now as far as I know it was on the plates - on our plates.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the plate was handed to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What order were you served - was the eldest served first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
There was no real - rule in that sense - just according to - see we sat our - in - in our own places but it just according to me mother's whim in that sense. I mean there was no fixed rule as to have it in ages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did the younger brothers and sisters said before they could feed themselves - can you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, the only thing is if - if they weren't walking - 'cos there'd only be own wouldn't have been walkin
g, well of course they'd have a high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who would feed that child? Would your mother feed it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I - can't tell you for I don't know. Might be any of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If you had any worries could you share them with her or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Any what? Well of course naturally I could, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was your father an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If you had any worries could you share them with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, you could share - could talk - talk to either of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents bring you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - yes. That I mean to say we were 
tell - just told to behave ourselves to one another. And naturally of course we help - we try and help one another in - in ways, but I don't know exactly how we did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It was more or less unconscious wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, I mean we just did - looked after - kept together, see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they say you should hit b}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 ack or not if another child hur}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 t you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know - well we never thought so I can't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You don't remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, Don't remember that 'cos - we never fought outside
 at all - we never - well we were very rare outside. Always stayed in the house mostly. See, me father wasn't keen on us playing in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you would grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh now I couldn't tell you that because you - you - they wouldn't know and I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Did they have any ambition for you - did your father want you to go on the docks with him or did he want you to get a better job than he had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Never interfered. No. He helped us 
as we - when we wanted it - and we - if - if we were looking for a job, I'm speaking of myself now - if I - got a job in an office, well - he didn't interfere. I took the job and he was quite satisfied, then when I went into a shoplife he - he helped me t
here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He didn't guide you in any way as far as your job was concerned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, he never interfered. Because of course he - he was working on his own work and of course he wouldn't know what the other work was.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents bring you up to consider certain things in life important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I couldn't tell you, only - only what I would to say to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 \endash }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624  to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
live as near to a Christian life as you could, that's what I'd say there. Because - I know this, that of a Sunday we - we all went to church. Or most of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Swearing? Was never allowed. And - and me father never did it. No. And he wouldn't allow us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If you did something that your parents did not like what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
According to the - according to what - how serious it was. Some times they'd shout at you, sometimes they'd give you advice or sometimes they'd give you thrashing - just according to what - what you'd done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who used to do it - your mother or your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Either of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember any particular occasion when you got a hiding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes. When I was with me brother and two - and two neighbours children - boy and a girl, brother and sis
ter, and we were told to go to Sefton Park. And we went to Sefton Park and we - we - of course we were only nippers - we went to Safton Park and then we went on to Garston Docks unknown. And of course next morning we got a row - we got a thrashing from me
 mother for going to Garston.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you think about that - were you badly done to or did you think you deserved it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Never bothered - I - never bothered over it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would you say that you received the ideas you had about how to behave from b
oth your parents or did one play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, they both - both - united together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When you had a birthday would it be a different day from any other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, because we never - we never recognised the birthdays, not then. Not at home we didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you receive any presents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Very, very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we would get - like friends of me father's and - or me mother's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 But there was none as far ay you were concerned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not as - we could always bring a friend in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I'm talking about on a birthday. There was nothing special on a birthday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, nothing special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Can you remember anything you did with your mother and father together on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well we were all together on Christmas Day. And of course we have - very rare we did have friends 'cos - we were such a big family. But - we had a very good Christmas. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Could you explain what the Christmas festivities were like? Did you have a big Christmas dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We had good Christmas dinner. We normally went to church in the Sunday monr - Christmas morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 All of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - what those - those that were able to go. They could never say exactly who went. But see we were brought up rather religiously.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you all stay at home on Christmas Day then - that was an understood thing was it
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any musical instruments in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We had a piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did anybody play it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I'm not too sure - I think me sister did but I'm not sure about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there anybody in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What sang - well I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So you had no musical evenings then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I couldn't say - I couldn't say that exactly how we did it there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You weren't a musical family? Did your parents play any games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes, but - it'd be draughts or anything like that. Or perhaps ludo.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Plenty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember your mother or father reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You mean publicly reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 People of your age, their parents often couldn't read at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh they were good readers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they used to read then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well occasionally they'd read but they didn't read regularly to us but they could do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they read aloud to you or to one another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't remember them reading aloud but they could do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Can you ever remember a funeral in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 A what? Only me mother's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who attended it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we all attended it as far as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have mourning clothes on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, we went in - as far as I know we went in our ordinary clothes. Or what - what you might call your best clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You would wear a black tie or a black band would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Occasionally.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who did you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that's hard to say. Might be a brother, it might be me father or it might be anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you ever taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Occasionally with me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever go out just with your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You don't remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember any other outings you had with your parents - on Bank Holidays or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. It never made no - any difference a Bank Holiday made no difference to us. Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well when I was about eleven. That was the only holiday that I know of from home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Albany. Near Halesby.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How long did you go for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Which members of the family went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Me brother and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you do when you got there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you have to know? We went more walking than anything else because it was a quiet country village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That was the only holiday you had while you were at school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Could you tell me how you spent Saturday in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - do a bit of cleaning and shop - what shopping was needed but Saturday was really much the same as any other day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Except that you didn't go to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Except - that's it - we didn't go to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you spend Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well chiefly to - Sunday school and church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any different clothes on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, yes, we had our be - what we call our best clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you play any games on a Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents think it wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Certainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents attend a place of worship or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes they did, that's why we went to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was it Church of England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Wesleyan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How often did your parents go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did both your mother and father go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I be - well me mother couldn't go - there was too many in the family - not often. But me father went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, there's one a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you generally go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Now 
that I couldn't tell you for now but we went - we did have a Sunday school - what we called a Sunday school treat but I couldn't tell you where we went to. It may have been a field in the park or it may not, I can't just tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What other social activities were organized by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we weren't in anything that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do what? Only - only for a few years 'til me voice broke.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What activities did you do in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only just sang - sang the - what was the - there was no activities.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there a choirmaster - did you go to choir practice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, went to choir practice once a year. Once a week I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have a cassock and surplice on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, they have surplice on in the Wesleyans.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the chapel run a temperance club?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Run a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Like the Band of Hope or anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes, most churches did in those days, they don't today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you a member of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, of the Band of Hope, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you do at the Band of Hope, anything important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, just occasional - occasional pat of recitation or - or perhaps a song, you don't know, but it was all temperance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to any other club organized by the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who said it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not re - not regularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, he would never tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you know your mother's views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember him voting in a general election at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He would vote but he never told us who he voted for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the same went for your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't remember me mother ever voting - there was no votes then for the women.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In some places at that time men felt they risked losing their job or their home if they
 voted differently from their employers, do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pres}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 sure, to vote for a particular }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, 'cos - he never - he never spoken for the vote himself so I don't know really what he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 He wasn't a member of a political party then was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents take part in any political activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When your parents were not doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your dad go to the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I could - couldn't tell you - be - sometimes he'd be having sleep and sometimes he'd read, you never know, 'cos it was a hard job.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he go out much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Occasionally but not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she ever go out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I - I never heard of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Anything connected with the church? When did your father get home from work in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Soon after five o'clock unless he was working late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well every - nearly every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father attend any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of. Only with me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he attend the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father or mother belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Like a boot club or a sick club or a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you get on with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we agreed very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there one you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that to say - we were all together.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 As a child who did you play with - your brothers - your sisters or with neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, with - our own family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you play - in the yard, the garden, the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Wherever we could I mean to say not in the street. But mostly in the household.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What games did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - in the house we'd play perhaps ludo or - games like that, or draughts. But out - at out - or going out we might have an iron hoop or perhaps - play marbles. But - we weren't out often, see. And if we did we more often went to the park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't remember getting dirty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you free to play with anyone you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well only our own family, we didn't mix with other families much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents discourage you from playing with certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't remember discouraging us but they never liked us playing in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to a youth organization?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 There was none then in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any hobbies at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Not that - I can't say I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you keep any pets or collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. No my life in - is - at the school was chiefly reading.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Reading was a hobby wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - it was. But I - I can't say what - well,
 I can't say what books I did read but most of them - I know of lot of them rather was Silas K Hawkins books. Yes. Oh he was a good - Fair Benny, yes. Tregeles Head - there was a lot - I know I lo - had nearly all of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 There were two brothers weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Two brothers. Then the - Silas - Silas was a high - a tall man. I knew - I didn't know him but I saw him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who was the one who used to write about Liverpool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Silas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was his brother's name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Joseph. Joseph. He was a
 lovely man too was Silas K Hawkins. He was tall - I only saw him once. And he was - really speaking he was - he was inviting me - to an aunt of mine for tea but - we were there - me brother and I was staying there at the time and of course they were - in
 those days they were strict that we didn't - we didn't have tea with them 'cos we were only lads - two young lads so of course they had it there - in the one room, they just let us - and we daren}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 t go to speak to them 'cos you - they were strict in that ca
se. But I did see him but only - not to speak to. Because the way they did - people above their station they did but - they were good otherwise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever go fishing or for walks?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. For a walk yes, but never fishing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever go cycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Cycling - only when I grew up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who did you go for walks with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Myself more often than not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624  go to any theatres, concerts, m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 usic halls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Or cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well there was only music halls and theatres in those days so - and we weren't allowed to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, yes, but you couldn't say much because things were cheap in those days and money was on the scarce side that you didn't get much.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember how much it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - usually - it was a penny a week and sometimes it was less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you spend that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh on sweets chiefly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If your mother was ill or confined to bed how did she manage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that I don't know. She'd have - she'd get somebody in but I couldn't tell you who it was or how she did it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You wouldn't know whether it was a relative or a friend or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It'd be perhaps a neighbour or a friend - I couldn't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You wouldn't know what happened when your younger brothers and sisters were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, well I wouldn't - I wouldn't know that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents have any relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well me father had his - his father and mother in Liverpool. But - and then I had an uncle in Liverpool on me mother's side - that's all the relatives I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How much did you see of them - did you see much of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well no not - well, me grandmother and grandfather, yes, I saw a good deal of them. But of me uncle I wouldn't say a good deal, he come when he - when he liked but we never knew when he was coming.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go to your grandmother's house or did they come to yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we - we'd go occasionally to me grandmother's house.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes, but they didn't often come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they share the same friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 As far as I know they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother have friends of her }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 own?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your father have friends of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were friends ever invited into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When, yes, at odd times but I couldn't say when.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If they were would they be offered anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well according to what time they came.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would they be invited to a bit of a party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, no we very - very rare had any party in the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 be}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
 invited say on the anniversary of a wedding or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we never celebrated - as far as I know they never celebrated an - their wedding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would you say that the friends invited in were your mother's friends or your father's friends or friends of both
? Not many people did come to your house did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did friends call in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I shouldn't imagine so because those houses were very big houses weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well in High Park Street, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And the old way of running from one house to the other didn't exist in High Park Street did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, it didn't exist there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 People used to keep themselves more to themselves didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. Much more. Well it's the same as here, with myself, I don't have people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What do you think your parents did when they got together with their friends or neighbours - did they sing, did they play cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Never played cards, I can tell you that, they never had cards but I can - don't know what - how they spent their evenings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Maybe just talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Just talk more than likely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Many people divide society into different social classes or groups. In that time before 1918 did you think of some people belonging to on
e and some to another group?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How do you mean that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you agree that people divided society into different social classes or groups? Do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I mean it didn't come to - in our home but I mean to say you're referring like
 that - generally people like - some people lived in a better house and you weren't wanted. Is that what you're trying to get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you think there were any different groups to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well there were but we didn't have anything to do with them
. I mean to say, anybody in the bet - in a better position well then naturally we wouldn't be wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What do you mean - you wouldn't be wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I mean to say if they were in the better position they would want the friends in their own position.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You lived near enough to Sefton Park to realize there were different groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Oh yes. There were different groups - well you weren't wanted in those places. Not with what - we were - we were classed as working people well you weren't wanted
 in those better houses. And even in Aigburth - if you got in - if you got to know anybody in Aigburth they wouldn't want you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You would reckon that you were working people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that would - we called ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What would you call the other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Snobs I suppose, chiefly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 There were working people and then the other people you'd call snobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well yes, because they always thought themselves better than other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What group did you belong to - you were the working people weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh I'd say working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of people belonged to the same group as yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we never had anything to do with them, we wouldn't know what they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who would you say were the working class people - people out to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well not - people that had a regular job but not a high paid job. I mean to say, if they had a high paid job they were - they considered themselves better than us. But - if they had a regular job well of course we were all classed much the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 A highly paid job - what kind of job would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - well it all - you see, like the head of a - a firm or anything like that. Well see they would naturally be above us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would you say a clerk was a better person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 W
ell a clerk you couldn't say because of course his - unless he was a f - a - in a good position he'd only be like as ourselves. 'Cos I mean in that case the wages would be much the same as - in the - elsewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Can you remember being brough}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624  up to treat people of one sort differently from people of another sort?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you ever told to touch your cap or show respect in some way to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we always did naturally if we - anybody came in we always tried to respect them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who would you do that to - anybody who came in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, anybody. We'd try and respect anybody even if their only our - only on our level. Or even if it was only - anybody above us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If you were out in the street would you touch your cap to anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, yes, naturally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well it was well - one more - only to somebody that we knew well that was like in a better position than us. Or - even - like women. I mean I - because now I'll tell you this - I don't because of cour
se I can't lift me hands up here you see - I should do - I try to do sometimes but I can't always raise me hand up. Well you see the point is I've got a slight rheumatism in me arm and of course I can't - see I can't lift it up high enough and I often - a
nd I use the left hand and even that sometimes is a bit stiff so of course I don't - I - I would normally if I saw people, especially ladies. But I can't always raise me hand up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there anybody you called Sir or Master?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well at - you'd naturally call your teacher Sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Or anybody - anybody - or anybody else, say if you were in an office or - or - anything like that, well, you'd call the - the gentlemen Sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember anyone showing this kind of respect to your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, no, I never remember - anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In the area were you lived who was considered the most important people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would it be the headmaster, the policeman, the postman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Minister - doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - the headmaster and - and the minister or the policeman we would treat with great respect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you come into contact with any of these people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well very rare. Very rarely. Except of course in - you'd see the minister but the point is you'd t
reat him with respect but he didn't always speak to you. But he were only - we were only the Saviours nippes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Why were they considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Now that's hard to say. We - we were just a tone - just to look at them as a tone of respect. And we treated them as that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And you don't know why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I couldn't say why, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember the shopkeepers in the area - who did they mix up with and the children of the shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that I couldn't tell you 'cos I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Did you ever take any notice of the clergy - the ministers of religion, the priests and other people like that, who did they mix up with do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I did - we had - the clergy - we called in the Wesleyan we call him the minister. But we'd treat him with respect or any minister.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who did he mix with? Who did he go out with when he wasn't in church - did he mix with you people or with his own group or what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that never - couldn't tell you that - me own - I - I don't remember - 
in the strict sense of the word him visiting us but I can't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Do you remember the teachers - who did they mix up with - did they mix amongst themselves or was there a teacher living in the street or did they live in the area or out of the area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Never knew where they lived. We went to school but we never knew where the teachers lived except the headmaster, we knew where he lived but he was - he lived in the Smithdown Road area. But - we never went to his house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 But they didn't mix up with you people did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You didn't know anything about farmers or employers - what sort of people would you say went to church - you went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of people went to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well in that sense you take - classing the church separate from the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I am yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well then we - I've had very little experience of the Church of Enaldn if that's what you're referring to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of people went to the Church of England? Were they richer people or poorer people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well it's according to where the church is. Because it it was a high class neighbourhood you - of course you'd reckon that the - the Church of England should be more of a high class but of course in some places its minister lowers h
imself as the saying is to the level of the people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of people went to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well as far as I know - business people and - humbler people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And that would be the same for the church also?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I suppose so, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where you lived did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say that there were various groups?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well it's hard to explain anything like that because it - it's according to - the housewife - what she provides.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It
 would depend on what the housewife had to provide as well you see? Would you say there was a different standard in High Park Street in the various houses, or was it all the same?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I couldn't tell you because you see we never met with - we never
 mixed with the people in High Park Street. We didn't - we hardly knew our next door neighbour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you know any group that was better off or worse off than yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well of the people round Princes Park and Sefton Park seemed to be better off than us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What about the people living round Mosely Street and all those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well they much - they're much the same as ours - same as - much as - the same as ours - they were - they lived their own life and unless of course you knew them they wouldn't have any to do with you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You wouldn't be able to describe the different families and their different ways of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh no, they wouldn't know how they lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were some families - do you think there was one group of people felt themselves better than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well naturally that is anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were some families thought of as rough and others as respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that I can't answer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You don't remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember any distinction of this kind between tradesmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I - well you would say there the tradesmen were - were - looked up to better than the - labourers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I think you'd find that right throughout wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, I think pretty well that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother and father have the same attitude to people in different classes and groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they never mentioned it - they never mentioned it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a particular social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well she never mentioned.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 But do you think she knew she belonged to the same class that you belonged to - the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that's hard to answer because I never heard her explain anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was it possible at that time to move from one class to another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well it was possible but whether they did it we don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you know any body who did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 an or a real lady?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well you would - there were several that yo
u would say were that. In fact I would - there was one lady - that I can - I can always say that she was a real lady - what we would call a real lady. She was reputed to be ninety-two - whether she was I don't know but she was a church lady - a church - a
 Church of England lady. I mean, her husband had been a - a vicar. And also - in her widowhood she'd go visiting the poorer people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And that's why you think she was a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I called her a real lady because she was trying to do good - to others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever meet a real gentleman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I have but I can't explain who they are or where they were. But I've heard of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you ever remember seeing a policeman round where you lived as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - not often. Not often - you would see a policeman but of course he'd only be on his beat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you think about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they're there to do their duty that's all I would say. We never had any trouble with them. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When you were naughty did your mother ever say to you I'll call a policeman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not as I know of. She'd thrash you or hit you - thrash you - she wouldn't - she never mentioned the police to you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How do you think the policemen treated the people in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well on the whole very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Everybody says the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, well of of course they do - they have to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Today it's entirely different isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well it's - it's different but the point is they have to be - try and be as fair as they can to everybody. T
hey haven't got an easy job, even today they haven't. But - even in olden days they - they tried to do their best and they were - on the whole they were respected.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, as far as I know we paid rent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever see the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you think about the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Some are good and some are bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember feeling that your parents had a struggle to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we - I - me father had a big struggle for many, many years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you think about that when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not that - I don't remember ever thinking about it. We just took if for granted.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I don't remember him being out of work. Only when there's the strike on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever get help from the guardians or the parish or any charity at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When there was someone in the district whom the people disapproved of very strongly was ther
e any special way in which they showed it - do you remember anyone being made to leave by rough music or was an effigy made or anything like that? I can find no trace of that in Liverpool - can you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What's that? Well I've heard about it. The only time - I've only seen it once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I would - I don't know what was happened but she was drummed out of the house-out of the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Drummed out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Drummed out, yes. By the neighbours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did they do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well the -
 I don't know what they did - what they did they got all sort of tin things and as the lady was moving out - they just rattled the tins, made a - I saw that. I don't know what street it was in but - I saw that and I burst out la}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 ghing '}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
os we - it so - it 
seemed such an unusual thing. See, evidently the lady wasn't liked and - when she was moving they drummed her out and it was the only time I've ever seen it done. Well I real - I saw it once but of course I was only in me early teens then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And you don't know what she did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
I've no idea - I didn't know the - nor did - I can't tell you what neighbourhood it was in. All I know is I saw it - I happened to be passing when I saw her being drummed out and - and they got all tins - all t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9710284\charrsid4212624 ins and things and made a terrib}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624  - terrible row 'til she got out of the street. I saw that once, but only once. And I don't know what neighbourhood I was in.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Five. As near as I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When you first started what time in the morning did you go and when did you come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I don't know - I wouldn't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You don't remember the school hours then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well the school hours - the normally - were - nine 'til twelve. Half past one to four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of school did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 A board school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well walked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was it a long way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Only a matter of - five to ten minutes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who went with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We often went on our own or perhaps with me own brothers and sisters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When you were a little child who took you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well wouldn't - I don't remember me going then but I must have done because I had a certificate when - when I was going - five years of age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you have your dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 At home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - I liked it all right and I plodded on until I got to ex seven. But otherwise I'd no trouble.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I got on very well with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the teachers emphasise certain things as}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7558505\charrsid4212624  important in life - manners, rea
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 diness, punctuality, ways of speaking - anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I don't remember them - explaining anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What do you think was the most important thing at school - punctuality or tidiness, manners, ways of speaking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I mean to say the - in school it should be manners and ways of speaking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If you did something the teachers did not like what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they ever punish the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I never heard them mention that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Don't you remember anybody getting the cane in your school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You got a cane odd times. You'd get a cane at odd times but - they was - on the whole that's all they ever did to you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were girls treated the same as boys in your school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't - they were separate so couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 As far as I know they did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they ask what you did at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That I couldn't tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I couldn't tell you whether they - us about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they meet the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 They knew the teachers - or they knew the headmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the other children come from similar types of home to yours or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well similar types.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not as a rule - not on the whole. The only thing is if they were - if - any were clever well they might be singled out to go 
for - for - a scholarship. But wouldn't make any difference otherwise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were scholarships very rare in your day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they weren't very great - but - there was like the - there was a scholarship every year and so many went in for it and of course
 some would pass and some didn't pass. But in the school I went to in 1890 my brother - well there was three went up - went in for science and maths scholarship. Two passed out of the three. And the other lad passed the general cert - general the followin
g year. And me brother was one of the - one that passed the first - the first year. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I don't remember it in our school at all - I went to a church school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh of course, this was in - in Upper Park Street and me brother and another lad won the - they were the only two that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7558505\charrsid4212624  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
won the science and art and then the other lad won the general scholarship next year and the headmaster was that pleased that the two passed out of three that he had it put up on the board in the school - had it all put up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they leave the school and go to another college then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. My brother went to - the Liverpool Institute. Yes, Mann Street. And then he finished up as a chartered accountant in - Australia. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not in - not that I know of. There was - there was no such a thing as gangs as we know it. Not as we know it today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any children who were left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I never knew of one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was this the only school you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. The only - I went to one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Tell me about ex seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I went from - from the infants in the one school right through to ex seven, that was the highest standard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Ex seven because they couldn't teach you anything else could they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not - not there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Fift - fourteen and nine months really. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That's unusual isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I - the - you were allowed to leave at fourteen occasionally could leave before. That was if - i
f the - there was something radical wrong - wrong at home like say if - say if the father or mother had died they would - if they were - if they had - had a job to go to they would be allowed to leave before they were fourteen. But normally it was fourtee
n. Well I was fourteen. Well I was fourteen and - nine months when I left school and I got an office job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Why did you stay there for nine months - did you like it so much?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well it was not that, it was the - I know - I could have left at fourteen
 but I hadn't a job to go to so I - I just kept on school 'til I could get a job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would you have stayed longer at school if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No I don't think so but - I might have done but of course I didn't think of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you attend any evening classes at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, for a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
No, it was - as far as I know I had a reasonable education, I don't say I had a - a college education, but I had a reasonable education, as much as they could give me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you think you benefited from school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 While you were at school did you have a part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You were unusual weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So you had none?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Never thought of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I'd like to ask about your first full time job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In an office. In an - an - in an insurance office for eighteen months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you get it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well was advertised in the Liverpool Mercury. That's the old paper. That would the advertising a paper - in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What exactly did you have to do in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Check the boo - check the collector's books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Nine to five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you work on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not Sunday but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Saturday 'til one o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I wasn't there long enough for one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was the wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Five shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you think it was a fair wage?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, it was average.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you give any of this money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
I gave it all to me - no, me mother wasn't living. I gave it to me father. No - wait a bit - no I didn't - wait a bit. I give it in the home because I had a step-mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It was spent on the home was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It was spent on the home, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you get on with the other people in the office?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you get on with the employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 With the what? Oh I got on with him all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh he was pretty good, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you like the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, it was rather good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did this job alter your attitude to school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. What do you mean to say -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you see the same schoolboys - your old friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh you mean after - after I left school. I never saw any of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So it might have changed your attitude to school? What job did you have after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I went in the grocery trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How long were you in that first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Eighteen months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Then you went in the grocery trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. I went in the grocery trade and stayed there all me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 All your life - in the same firm?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, in three different firms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What were the hours in the grocery trade in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Eight - eight to half past seven. No 
half holiday. And on a Friday eight - eight o'clock till ten - that's ten o'clock at night and to eleven o'clock on a; Saturday. No half holiday at the time - they'd - they did later on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What were the wages then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Very poor. Very -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What made you go into it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I just fan tied it that was all. Only of course I didn't realize it was such as paid com - paid trade. It's very - it's very little pay.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Is it still a badly paid trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well not at present, I believe it's much better now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And you were in that job until you retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 'Till I retired, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would you have preferred any other type of job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I never give it thought. It would have been better if I'd have gone on a better job but of course I didn't think o
f it at the time. And then of course what I made a mistake there I got myself a bound apprentice so I couldn't leave. Yes. So I couldn't leave.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Which firm was that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Pegreams.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You would be a manager very early in life then wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Like you mean an inspector in the area or do you mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Manager - a shop manager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well you were - well I was a shop manager after - years after. Oh yes, I was a - and I was a shop manager - from about twenty-five 'til I went in the Army o
n the first world war. I went in the Army - that's what gave - I gave up the - I gave up the grocery trade then. Well I had to. Well I did. I gave up then I went back again into it. Because, see, when I came out of the Army - they didn't take the men back
 
so of course I was out of work. See they wouldn't pay up - they would give us the wages we wanted. In fact they wouldn't give you living wage. Well so I went labouring for eighteen months. And then of course when - after - I was in Sunlight for the last s
ix months and then - there was a strike between two unions and we had to come out - I never went back, I got a job - a job at Pe - Coopers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was that Lever Brothers you were working at?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Lever Brothers. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That was when you were labouring - what kind of work were you doing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I was on the mill. Well I was in the labouring on - in the mills.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you like that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not much. But still I stuck it while - while I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you live over that side then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was the wages like at Levers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well wages were fair in - in the - in the Sunlight. They were fair - they weren't too good but they were - were fair - they were better than in the shops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 But you went back to the shops because there was no industrial unrest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well there was the industrial unrest and of course - I didn't - I didn't want to be out of work and I was - as far as I know I was the only one of two thousand that got a job. Yes. And they couldn't understand why I got it but of course 
I was in - I knew me trade. See I'd been in the goods trade and I knew it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And you served an apprenticeship to it didn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to a trade union at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only while I was in the labouring - labouring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you take part in any of it's activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Employers and the workers? No. Not as a rule. They were - separate to one another in a sense. They had no connection with one another.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest amongst the workers themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What do - now what's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You told me there was a dispute between to trade unions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 So that would indicate that there were divisions interest among the working people themselves weren't there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers - did you think that was so?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well you couldn't - you
 - you had to do what the union told you, I mean you had no will - no willpower of your own. You - in fact you knew nothing about it - it happened in my life twice. That I - there's dispute between two unions on two occasions. And it affected me on - in -
 
'cos in the first place, see I lived over the water, well I - a friend of mine got me a job in Princess Candle Works. Well I stuck it for three months, it was too heavy I had to give it up. Well I got a job then in Cover Claytons - a lab - a fitter's labo
u
rer. Well we came - they came out on strike - a dispute between two unions - we had nothing to do with it. Well - they settled - I know - I didn't - in between I got in on Sunlight. I didn't go back to Clover Claytons. Well Sunlight I was in about six mon
t
hs and the same thing happened. The dispute between two unions. Well on - when they settled it - it - they - well, before they settled it they gave us all - they said - they - they said there was two thousand but how many I don't know but there was a lot 
o
f us, they said two thousand. They gave us a week's notice. And I was the only one that had a job to go to. See what I did - it was - I was on nights that week and - when I got home I said to me wife, 'course she hadn't got up then but I went up to her an
d
 I said, they've given us - they've given us a week's notice. She said, well never mind, she said, get your breakfast then come to bed. I said, no, I said, I'm getting me breakfast and then, I said, I'm going to look for a job. So she didn't interfere and
 
I went to Coopers. I didn't know whether I'd get on but I went on spec. 'cos I knew like - I knew the trade. I got on taken right away. Well I served me week at Sunlight because it was - I was going for less money at Coopers. But still I did - it was a re
gular job so of course I stuck it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It was a cleaner job too wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well it - I was better because I was there for twenty-one years then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you think there was a difference between craftsmen and other workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Between what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Between a tradesman and a labourer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 There was a difference yes, because - the labourer is only only helping the - the tradesman. Just handing him his tools and that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Would you say that full time work changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
I don't know. It's just according to which - what you're doing. That's hard to say because I mean to say if you didn't like your job you would naturally want to leave - if you could get the chance. And yet of course you might find a job that - you're we
ll pleased with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of job would you have liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well I don't know. I - I've often thought I'd liked to have learnt the joinery. But - I didn't do so what I - I often thought I'd have liked to because I like to try and potter in - in w
oodwork. I'm not good at it - I do little odd - well I don't do anything now but I used to do little odd jobs. But - I don't know anything about it really. And of course I never had the proper tools to do a proper job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And they were so expensive weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well that's a fact but - I've often thought - I wish I'd have been a joiner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you continue to live at home after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes. Until I got - 'til I - 'til I left home and then of course I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It made no - no indifference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Any difference with your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you spend your Sunday differently - did you still go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
You told me earlier how you spent your spare time - did you spend your spare time still the same after you left school - staying at home playing with your sisters and brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Or did you go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I went out but not a great deal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go out in the evenings much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not a lot - only to a - a religious meeting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who did you go with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well more often myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you make any new friends - boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I had friends but not many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you meet them? At the job or in the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh in the job where I'd be at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you bring these friends home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, I could do - I didn't often but I did do at times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any special friends at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No boys or girl friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not the - not the - at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only if I took 'em home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your parents expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they did know where I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have to be home at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, well, ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Even after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. Ten o'clock was me time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What age were you when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Twenty-two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How long had you known your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 About eighteen months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In the mission hall.
