ell I'd been in two or three houses 'til 1918 - I don't know how many. See however the job was - see I was in Sea - working in - I worked in Seacombe for four years and then I got a job in Rock Ferry and I was there for twenty years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You were in Rockferry for twenty years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
