\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any relatives to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well me wife's relatives, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they come and help you?
