 I was twenty-four shillings a week. When I got - when I got on in Coo - in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11615031\charrsid4212624 P}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
egrams, I - when I got the job as manager - I was - got thirty shillings a week.
