\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In those days, yes, was good money - well - it was not - it was not big money but; we -
