\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How much of your earnings would you give to your wife at that time when you were first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7305616 
