\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Cleaning, cooking - washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well any - I used to do odd jobs in the house and I can - when I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - yes, only the latter years though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What? No, no not really, not any repairs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you help with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Dressing and undressing and bathing them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 I always do that Reg - when they were small I did that. I washed them and she wiped them. We did that between us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you read aloud to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 After - after -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Tell them stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we had a - well I suppose you would tell the stories like ordinary conversation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you take them out without their mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not as a rule. We all went together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you look after the children when the mother was out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, if - if it was necessary, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any regular tasks for the children to do as they grew older to help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we never told them to they used to
 - me wife did most of the - the - the jobs to be done but the children helped wherever they could - but there was no strict rule as what they should do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What timed would the children go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - early at seven o'clock and then when they got a bit older it would be nine o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they put themselves to bed or did you or your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh they'd go to bed themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did the children share a bed or a bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - the girl was in a separate room and the two lads are together in the other room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Then you and your wife were in the third room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have a room for bathing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We had no bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you manage then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - by - buy a bath and that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When did the children have clean clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - every week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where were the meals eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did they eat? In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any times when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11615031\charrsid4212624 ha}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 t? No, not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did your wife cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In the back kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she have a range or a gas cooker?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Gas cooker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When was breakfast eaten? Did you go out before the children got up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, I went - I was - up first and I - more often out first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That would mean that your wife and children would have breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did they usually have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - ba - bacon, or if the eggs were reasonable - bacon and egg.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have anything different on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not for breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 But for other meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
No, only the - no, not exactly - just like - a proper dinner and sometimes a manage for tea but we never knew exactly what we had. Sometimes it'd be a tin of something or anything what you fancied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have your dinner when you came home from work at night time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - yes and no, for a - for a time - I went home for me dinner the midday. But we had - when we were living nearer but when I lived away from the shop, well I had it - I had to wait 'til night time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your wife make any bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Occasionally but not regular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she make any pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. No, you asked that question yesterday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did she make any medicines or bottle fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have fresh vegetables or tinned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Have what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you grow your own vegetables or did you buy them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We couldn't - we had no garden so we couldn't grow them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have tinned or dried vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not dried.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Tinned? Tinned and fresh I suppose. Did you keep hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How many times did you have meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Meat? Well every - every dinner time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was it tinned meat or fresh meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Fresh meat. 'Cos things weren't so dear then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your wife ever go short so you or the children could have more?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have larger helpings of food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not that I know of. That I can't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were the children allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well, yes, if you wanted to ask a question certainly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were they allowed to choose what they wanted to eat from what was cooked or did they have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well if they - it was on the table what was there and they had what they wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was your attitude if they left some food uneaten on their plates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they never did it.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they have to wait for things on the table to be offered to them or did they have to ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they - no, they could help themselves. You asked me all these questions yesterday.. I can't understand w
hy you want all these questions. I can't quite see 'cos you - there's such a number of questions that I can't understand. To me they're all - most of them are unnecessary that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 We're trying to find out if there's any difference in the way your parents brought you up and how you brought up your children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well of course I can't - I can't say that, I mean to say, - it - I brought me children up as I thought was right and they had the - they had the free used of everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You brought your children up as your parents brought you up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, I suppose I - I suppose that is it really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And also the association of your wife would make it slightly different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, well we shared the same - shared it all together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If they asked for a second helping could they have one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, if they wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they have to hold their knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh no, they always - they always used it in the ordinary way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were they allowed to bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not during meals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When did the members of the family leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When did what? When they - when we'd finished the tea. Or when we finished the meal really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did all the family present for the meal sit at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Oh yes. I know, and I'll tell you another thing which I still don't understand. If we did have company which is not very often and there was two or three children which of course you - with relatives that's possible - they had meals not at our table
 but in there at the same time in the - perhaps the corner. Well that - it was my - that was what I did because I objected to them waiting so instead of them waiting I - I had boxes - well of course I put them, I didn't have leave them there together but 
I'd bring the box perhaps from where I kept me wood - two or three boxes and they sat on the boxes and I give 'em - their meals there. They - they had it the same time as us.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And enjoyed it more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they did, yes. But you - you take it in the 
ordinary sense - if you - if you don't let them sit down at - with you of course if there's - if there's a lot there you can't always but you put it separate table at the same time your full meal is done with together. And you're not worried about them - 
they'll look - they'll look and see - looking at you to see if they can - hurry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who was the meal served by?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well chiefly me wife.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No special order.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What method did you have of feeding and seating the children who were too young to feed themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - it according to where - where we put 'em. If they were in the high chair they'd be near the - near me wife or - or near - or if they were like too old for their high chair well they'd be - sit perhaps by me or by
 her. It's according to circumstances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When your children were young did you feel there was a right way or a wrong way of bringing up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - certainly the right way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you and your wife have the same ideas about bringing up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you talk about this - did you discuss it between yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I don't know because we were both of the same religion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there anyone you used to talk - to if you were worried about the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was there anybody to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If the child was ill or anything did you talk to anybody - you had no mother, could you ask your wife'}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11615031\charrsid4212624 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624  mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well at times, we'd have - we'd have the wife's mother or perhaps he sister. But I mean to say, we - you were - the
y didn't live near us so of course we'd have to let them know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your mother-in-law alive when your children were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How often did you see her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - they lived in Liverpool and we lived o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11615031\charrsid4212624 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624  - out on the other side of the river. Therefore which was - you never knew.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever ask her advice about bringing up the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not - no no}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11615031\charrsid4212624 t }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 that - not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you think she had the same ideas that you had about bringing up children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When the children were little did you ever manage both to go out and leave them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. We didn't believe in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Even if you had somebody to look after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, because we - we used to look after them ourselves, we never went out without them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you let your children join in when grown ups were talking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes, if we - if they wanted to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you bring your children up to consider most important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I suppose to live - to live honestly and straightforward I'd say there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you tell your children to hit back or not if another child hurt them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, we wouldn't tell them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any other children you discouraged them from playing with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not that I know of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If your children did something you disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If they what? If they didn't like what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 If your children did something you didn't approve of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh - well according to how - what - because I only ever hit one - my younge
st lad once. They never had a real thrashing and the only time it was he brushed some bread on the floor and I said, pick it up. And he wouldn't. And I made him pick it up because I knew that I had to be master. But they never got a thrashing otherwise. A
nd that only happened once in his life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
That's the only time you can remember hitting them? Would you say that your children received the ideas they had about how to behave from both their parents or did one of them play a more important part than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, we took practically together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Your wife did not work after she had children did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. Only when - only during the first world war when I was away. She had to do then. Because they didn't give you enough to live on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What was she doing then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 She was working in - a hospital. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 The kiddies would be about eight and nine wouldn't they then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Nine, eleven and thirteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 It was a trying time wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, very - well you - you only got twenty-nine s
hillings and you had to do everything with it. So of course she had to go to work. There was no choice in it. I was away so I just couldn't - had no choice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you feel about leaving the children when she had to work - you didn't like it at all did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I didn't like it but then I was away from home as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Some people think that children should be with their mother all the time, others think it is not necessary and does them good to be with other people quite a lot, what do you think about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Well - we may - the mother should be with them pretty well all the time 'cos of course the father goes to work. But when they - when the works over, well the father should take his share which we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When your children had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only that you'd send them a card.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you give them a present at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Often we did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they have a little party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they have friends in or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not - not as a rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Can you remember what you and your wife did on Christmas Day with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we - she cooked the dinner, I sat quietly 'cos I - I'd worked all hours the last - the week before. I worked 'til - I worke
d 'til - often half past ten at night, so of course my Christmas Day I was tired. And I had to sit quiet to keep myself up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever take the children out on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we - we never went out anywhere, or very, very rarely. Very rare. We had Christmas at home more often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any musical instruments in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 A piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Any other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Any what? No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did anybody play the piano?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Me daughter did for a time but - not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did anybody sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well we could all sing to a certain extent, we never - no - on grea one singing then anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you play any games with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - well while they were young yes, but not when they got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your wife join in the games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 The whole lot of you used to play games together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What kind of games would they be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they were - draughts - something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were there any books or newspapers or magazines in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well there were plenty of books but no - no - rarely a magazine but we - we didn't get a weekly - a daily paper. We got a weekly paper.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to the library at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, we were too far away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you read aloud to each other or to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did I what? At times, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were the children taken out visiting neighbours, friends or relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were they taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were they what? Well they - they could go shopping on their own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 They were not taken then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 But there's no need of us taking them shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever take the children out by yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Can you tell me what happened on a Bank Holiday - did you ever take the children out on a Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes - we'd take 'em both - take 'em both out - we were all out. All out together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you go as a rule on a Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Seacombe san - Seacombe shore.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you ever go away on a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Only the later few - the last few years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 For how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 A - a week 1 sometimes a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You went every year did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Not every year. - it's according for circumstances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Where did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well to somewhere in North Wales usually.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you like North Wales?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you all go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Used to all go together, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you do when you got there - was it a quiet country place?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well a quiet country place, yes. They just joined in with any - I mean you just - walked round or did what you fancied. The
re was no rule anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Can you tell me how you spent Saturday in those days - you were working weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 In a shop - I was working 'til eleven o'clock so I couldn't do anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How did you spend Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Go to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you or the children put on different clothes on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I - you don't expect us to go in our working clothes to church do you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you think it wrong to work or enjoy yourself on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes, certainly it's wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you allow your children to play games on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You did attend a place of worship didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 And it was Methodist - Presbyterian then wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No it wasn't - it was Baptist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How often did you go on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - morning and night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your wife go with you too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did either of you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did this church or chapel run any temperance }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11615031\charrsid4212624 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 lub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not that I know - of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to any clubs organized by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your children go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did they go to any adult or family services at the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well they go - it was an adults service of a morning but they - they would go then and the - and the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 What did you say Rag? Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have family prayers at your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were your children taught to say prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Who taught them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Their mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you have any views at all on politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Not particularly. I never both - never had - had any strict political views, I just voted for whoever I thought was best. Never - I never hesitated, I never stuck to any certain - lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 You voted for the individual rather than the party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your wife thing the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Yes. Pretty much the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Do you remember voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I can't tell you that - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you or your wife ever feel under any pressure from anybody to vote for a particular party? Your employer for example.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well I mean to say they would - they might influence - they might try to influence us but they never - never - never did it.
 As far as I know they never spoke about politics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Were you ever a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you take part in any political activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When you and your wife were not doing your work how did you spend your time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Not doing the work? Well we just - what we fancied. Perhaps we'd sit down, read, perhaps we'd do a little - perhaps I'd do a little job that I wanted to do. Or or we may read - we'd both read together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go out together in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 That's before the children were born? The whole lot of you went out together - the children as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well - not always because of course the children had their own - own places to go to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go out often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 When did you get home from work in the evenings?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 
Half past seven to eight. Well the hours were eight 'til half past seven. Ten o'clock on a Friday and eleven o'clock Saturday. So you couldn't go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 How many evenings a week did you spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Well every - every evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you go to any clubs, institutes or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did your wife belong to a club or institute?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did you belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Like a boot club, sick club, funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Did either of you take park in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No, not really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6500729 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 Cricket, football, fishing, shooting, cycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3476491 TB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4130372\charrsid4212624 No.
